---
title: SuperQuick Turkey Tikka Bowls with Quick-Cook Basmati Rice and Garlic Flatbreads
description: Spice up your dinner with this vibrant tikka bowl! Juicy turkey gets coated in bold Indian spices, pan-seared to perfection, then tossed with sweet roasted red pepper for a burst of flavour. Served alongside fluffy basmati rice and warm garlic flatbread, this speedy 15-minute meal is as tasty as it is convenient.

